  content: 'That tagline definitely adds a layer of humor and helps explain the core gameplay loop.  It connects the unusual title "BEDNOMANCER" to the act of getting the kittens back to sleep.  The play on words with "unbed" is clever and memorable.\n' +
    '\n' +
    "Here's why it works:\n" +
    '\n' +
    '* **Clarifies the Gameplay:** It directly explains what the player does in the game.\n' +
