    '* **Creates Intrigue:**  It still retains a bit of the mystery and quirkiness of the title.\n' +
    '* **Reinforces the Title:** It helps players understand and remember the connection between "BEDNOMANCER" and putting the kittens to sleep.\n' +
    '\n' +
    '\n' +
    `Using this tagline alongside strong visuals and a clear description of the game on your Steam page would significantly improve players' understanding of what "BEDNOMANCER" is all about.  It could be a winning combination!\n`,
